42:33.626 --> 42:36.277
♪<i> When they crucified </i> ♪

42:36.296 --> 42:38.888
♪<i>   My Lord? </i> ♪

42:39.040 --> 42:40.615
(inhales deeply)

42:40.633 --> 42:42.225
♪<i> Were you there</i> ♪

42:42.452 --> 42:44.894
♪<i> When they crucified </i> ♪

42:45.046 --> 42:48.472
♪<i>   My Lord? </i> ♪

42:48.567 --> 42:50.266
♪<i> Oh, sometimes</i> ♪

42:50.493 --> 42:53.978
♪<i> It causes me to tremble</i> ♪

